<p><span class="anchor" id="p28"></span>استتار الْحرم<a href="#p28" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p29"></span>فَإِن كن مستترات لم يجز الرمى<a href="#p29" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p30"></span>قيل<a href="#p30" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
