<p><span class="anchor" id="p33"></span>وَالأَصَح عدم اشْتِرَاط ذَلِك<a href="#p33" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p34"></span>وَلَو عزّر ولى<a href="#p34" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p35"></span>مَحْجُوره<a href="#p35" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
